Dialogue: 5,0:00:03.73,0:00:05.37,Default,,0,0,5,,You looking, Ai?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:09.10,0:00:10.76,Default,,0,0,5,,This is my village.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:19.40,0:00:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:22.29,0:00:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:24.45,0:00:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it looks just like Heaven?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:27.21,0:00:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Heaven?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:28.46,0:00:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:29.49,0:00:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a place in the skies, where the dead go.{PV}
Dialogue: 5,0:00:31.38,0:00:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A dreamland filled with \Nfriendship and happiness.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:35.89,0:00:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to make this village a place just like Heaven.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:40.28,0:00:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,In these hellish times, a place like that \Nwould be a beacon of hope for everyone.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:46.10,0:00:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna help!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:47.52,0:00:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:50.96,0:00:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Ai...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:52.80,0:00:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is {\i1\fs54}my{\i0\fs55} dream—and my job.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:57.05,0:01:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, you should find a dream of your own.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:01.04,0:01:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
