Dialogue: 5,0:03:03.70,0:03:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:07.64,0:03:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean to say you're following me \Nwithout knowing even {\i1\fs54}that{\i0\fs55}?{are you following me without even knowing that?}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:11.29,0:03:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}You're{\i0\fs55} the one who took me with you!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:13.84,0:03:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,"Where are we going?" Nowhere.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:17.04,0:03:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All we're doing is searching for Hana.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:21.31,0:03:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She was strangely ignorant
Dialogue: 5,0:03:23.52,0:03:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but always so expressive.{very expressive? emotive?}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:25.85,0:03:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd laugh and cry and get pissed off{ with all she had}, \Nand she ate everything in sight.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:30.27,0:03:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We were together for almost six months,
Dialogue: 5,0:03:33.24,0:03:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and then she vanished without a trace.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:35.93,0:03:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you abandoned?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:38.03,0:03:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I was.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:41.16,0:03:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This all happened over ten years ago, when the world was at its worst.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:46.04,0:03:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll probably be that much older, now.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:49.41,0:03:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you gonna do when you find her?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:51.89,0:03:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That depends.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:57.68,0:04:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If she needs me, I'll do my best to {offer her a }help{ing hand} her.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:01.20,0:04:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But if she's found her own happiness,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:03.52,0:04:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just look at her from afar \Nand be on my way.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:05.49,0:04:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there's always \Nthe chance she's already dead.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:09.60,0:04:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There's also something else I'm searching for.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:13.15,0:04:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:16.20,0:04:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In any age, there's only one thing all immortals crave.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:20.92,0:04:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm searching for a way to die.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:26.65,0:04:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A way... to die?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:29.10,0:04:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:30.66,0:04:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to die?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:33.42,0:04:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed I do.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:36.35,0:04:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I... love humans.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:39.77,0:04:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? Become the last human alive?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:42.78,0:04:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta be kidding me.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:45.05,0:04:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The last human...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:52.48,0:04:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, "the last human." \NWrap your head around that phrase!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:56.30,0:04:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you try imagining it!{PV}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:58.77,0:05:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The last living human!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:01.23,0:05:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that sound like a good life?!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:03.39,0:05:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There'd be no one around. No one.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:05.58,0:05:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be all by myself, forever!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:08.51,0:05:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever and ever... and ever.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:26.16,0:05:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you scared?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:28.91,0:05:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're scared of becoming that, aren't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:36.65,0:05:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why you'd rather be a monster?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:44.08,0:05:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:49.05,0:05:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's happening?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:51.41,0:05:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch. I screwed up.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:52.58,0:05:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:20.01,0:06:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:21.00,0:06:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to talk!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:23.23,0:06:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri, you saved me?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:25.46,0:06:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget that{,} and stop talking!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:42.58,0:06:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How did I...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:46.92,0:06:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, just put this on.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:49.40,0:06:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That jerk!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:51.18,0:06:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:52.50,0:06:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on! Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:55.01,0:06:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna kill him!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:56.93,0:06:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What he did {\i1\fs54}saved{\i0\fs55} you!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:58.68,0:07:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What? But...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:01.20,0:07:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,After he kicked you off the bridge, \Nthat place turned into a battlefield.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:06.06,0:07:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did that?!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:07.72,0:07:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Humpnie did.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:09.56,0:07:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:10.97,0:07:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If he suspects he's about to be ambushed,
Dialogue: 5,0:07:12.86,0:07:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll launch a suicide attack...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:17.50,0:07:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,taking everything with him.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:21.47,0:07:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so ridiculous!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:23.22,0:07:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You can say that again.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:24.92,0:07:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's true he saved you \Nfrom getting caught up in it.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:30.27,0:07:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He may seem coldhearted, \Nbut he doesn't commit meaningless acts of violence.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:35.22,0:07:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how unfair his actions seem,
Dialogue: 5,0:07:38.22,0:07:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,he's definitely got a method to his madness.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:44.35,0:07:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I find that very hard to believe.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:48.56,0:07:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the only reason he turned out this way
Dialogue: 5,0:07:51.86,0:07:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,is that he was burdened with the fate of immortality.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:55.64,0:08:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But even with that fate, he was better off \Nback when he was with the woman he loved.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:14.41,0:08:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mother!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:20.72,0:08:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dad's called Humpnie Humbert.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:24.60,0:08:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll come see you someday.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:29.07,0:08:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So he really {\i1\fs54}is{\i0\fs55} my father, isn't he?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:35.10,0:08:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did he go?!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:38.08,0:08:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He was kidnapped.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:39.86,0:08:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:40.72,0:08:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All signs point to it.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:42.58,0:08:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He was facing about seven people.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:44.96,0:08:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And they were deliberately using \Nrubber bullets to avoid killing him{ normally used to suppress riots}.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:48.50,0:08:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Rubber bullets?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:49.59,0:08:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever Humpnie dies, \Nhe resurrects to a completely healthy state.{the doctor???}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:53.25,0:08:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna beat him,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:54.93,0:08:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,you've gotta capture him \Nwithout inflicting a fatal wound.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:59.72,0:09:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to save him!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:01.89,0:09:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My spare underwear!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:09.40,0:09:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll manage to get through it himself, somehow.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:11.80,0:09:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, he {\i1\fs54}is{\i0\fs55} an immortal monster{, after all}.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:15.11,0:09:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not a monster!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:17.49,0:09:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, he may be cruel,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:19.65,0:09:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but he can get surprisingly lonely{ sometimes}, \Nand he only pretends to be the bad guy, so...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:24.10,0:09:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So... I've gotta save him, \Nor he'll only get more twisted!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:29.17,0:09:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He already seriously considers himself a monster.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:34.22,0:09:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:35.76,0:09:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,he is {\i1\fs54}not{\i0\fs55} a monster!{PV}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:44.13,0:09:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear ya.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:45.56,0:09:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never call him one again.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:49.37,0:09:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Yuri Sakuma Dmitriyevich.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:00.32,0:10:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Ai.{i typo'd this as "I'm I"...}{rofl}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:05.79,0:10:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's get going.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:07.60,0:10:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:08.37,0:10:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're coming with me?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:11.31,0:10:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, after he went and called me his friend, how could I {\i1\fs54}not{\i0\fs55}?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:21.78,0:10:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pleasant surprise, Ai.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:42.52,0:10:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally up, Humpnie Humbert?{PV}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:45.79,0:10:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{part b}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:47.93,0:10:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you bastards?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:50.21,0:10:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Did we forget to introduce ourselves?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:53.12,0:10:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess you did.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:54.17,0:10:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:56.10,0:10:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Hiko,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:57.42,0:10:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm a huge fan of yours!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:00.04,0:11:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So, is it true that when you \Ndie under extreme trauma,
Dialogue: 5,0:11:03.39,0:11:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,you lose your memories of it?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:05.68,0:11:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:06.84,0:11:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd you hear that?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:10.50,0:11:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}Damn it! I can't remember!{Keep this comment: it's not "i can't remember because these guys did something to me". it's "i can't remember what these guys did to me"}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:13.48,0:11:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}What the hell did these guys do to me?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:16.32,0:11:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck off,
Dialogue: 5,0:11:17.48,0:11:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,you assholes!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:20.25,0:11:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Got some new insults, I see!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:22.11,0:11:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:23.40,0:11:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Damn it!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:25.12,0:11:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Recognize the outfit?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:27.57,0:11:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Should look just like yours.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:29.29,0:11:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you!{x3}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:31.66,0:11:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna kill you!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:32.78,0:11:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've ever \Nwanted to be someone else.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:36.59,0:11:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is with you guys?!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:38.53,0:11:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:39.63,0:11:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... I can probably take care of looking like you,
Dialogue: 5,0:11:43.34,0:11:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but that immortality thing's gonna be a bitch.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:45.64,0:11:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why—
Dialogue: 5,0:11:46.70,0:11:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,—you died?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:49.49,0:11:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You gave up your life just to capture an idiot like me?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:54.21,0:11:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a real friggin' dumbass!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:57.28,0:12:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That spirit of yours is just awesome.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:00.13,0:12:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You destroy evil \Nwithout even uttering a word
Dialogue: 5,0:12:02.42,0:12:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and wield that dark justice of yours \Nwhile you kill people.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:06.35,0:12:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I know each and every thing about you!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:09.20,0:12:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna die, don't you, Humpnie Humbert?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:11.25,0:12:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna take back the death God stole from you, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:16.70,0:12:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:18.42,0:12:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:23.97,0:12:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get me wrong.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:25.34,0:12:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Dying isn't my wish.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:28.64,0:12:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:29.98,0:12:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:31.42,0:12:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you lying when \Nyou said you wanted to die?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:34.40,0:12:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you deceive me?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:36.13,0:12:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I didn't {\i1\fs54}lie{\i0\fs55}.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:38.38,0:12:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:39.92,0:12:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:41.22,0:12:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't lie to me, would you?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:44.60,0:12:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is something I've never told anyone.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:48.11,0:12:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell {\i1\fs54}you{\i0\fs55}, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:51.50,0:12:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't just want to die.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:54.91,0:12:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I... want to die {\i1\fs54}happy{\i0\fs55}.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:59.89,0:13:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like I've been doing for others,
Dialogue: 5,0:13:02.56,0:13:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I want someone to see me off.{care me for on my death bed}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:04.45,0:13:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}S-Stop it.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:05.32,0:13:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My friends, my wife, and my kids—
Dialogue: 5,0:13:09.06,0:13:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to make the people who'll live on after me \Ncry and lament my loss,
Dialogue: 5,0:13:13.07,0:13:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,as I leave behind just a little bit of regret
Dialogue: 5,0:13:14.45,0:13:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}N-No...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:15.57,0:13:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}No way!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:16.91,0:13:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and die.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:20.65,0:13:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:23.44,0:13:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}That's{\i0\fs55} your wish?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:25.81,0:13:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna die an ordinary, worthless death like that?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:28.67,0:13:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody in this world can have that wish granted, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:32.84,0:13:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:35.02,0:13:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish to live a life of happiness
Dialogue: 5,0:13:37.80,0:13:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and die a happy man!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:42.59,0:13:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:43.47,0:13:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're betraying me?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:45.37,0:13:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,After being everything I wanted{ to be},
Dialogue: 5,0:13:48.30,0:13:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,you're gonna betray me now?!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:51.28,0:13:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I care. Dumbass.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:58.73,0:14:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:02.59,0:14:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You can just become our plaything.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:07.10,0:14:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill ya!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:08.73,0:14:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep provokin' me{,} and I'll keep killin' ya!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:11.33,0:14:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, then.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:12.66,0:14:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But {\i1\fs54}I'll{\i0\fs55} be the one who laughs last.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:25.53,0:14:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleased to make your acquaintance, everyone.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:27.32,0:14:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come to bury you.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:32.33,0:14:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A gravekeeper?!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:34.36,0:14:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Scar!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:35.93,0:14:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I say we could barge in \Nonly {\i1\fs54}after{\i0\fs55} checking things out?!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:39.63,0:14:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We gravekeepers pride ourselves on our efficiency.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:42.40,0:14:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:43.48,0:14:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the hell did you come here?!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:45.50,0:14:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,To save you, of course!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:47.97,0:14:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid?!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:48.91,0:14:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This has got nothing to do with you!{ Leave!}{strangers need not apply!}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:50.28,0:14:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It does too!{i'm not a stranger!}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:52.32,0:14:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:53.77,0:14:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It {\i1\fs54}does{\i0\fs55} have something to do with me!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:57.29,0:14:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you saying?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:59.50,0:15:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother was beautiful and childish
Dialogue: 5,0:15:02.94,0:15:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and always so expressive.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:05.33,0:15:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd laugh and cry and get pissed off{ with all she had}, \Nand she ate everything in sight.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:11.81,0:15:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She sucked at whistling and at cooking, too, \Nbut she was great at cleaning.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:16.81,0:15:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't have a way with words,{had strange word usage}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:19.24,0:15:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,she hated cigarettes and perfume,
Dialogue: 5,0:15:21.97,0:15:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and she really liked sweets,
Dialogue: 5,0:15:24.92,0:15:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:29.41,0:15:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,she loved you.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:40.02,0:15:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hana.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:47.68,0:15:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Ai.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:50.12,0:15:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a man called Humpnie Humbert
Dialogue: 5,0:15:53.13,0:15:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and a gravekeeper called Alfa,
Dialogue: 5,0:15:56.28,0:15:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm their daughter.{i'm the daughter born to a man called humpnie and a gk called alfa}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:58.16,0:16:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're{...} my...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:03.66,0:16:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:05.23,0:16:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the kid of \Na human and a gravekeeper,
Dialogue: 5,0:16:07.55,0:16:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}and{\i0\fs55} you're Humpnie's daughter?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:09.73,0:16:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just too funny!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:13.46,0:16:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You are all filthy.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:18.74,0:16:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, Yuri, and Scar weren't all that different, were they?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:24.93,0:16:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"A place in the skies, where the dead go."
Dialogue: 5,0:16:28.96,0:16:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The villagers just didn't want to let go of their Heaven.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:34.70,0:16:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they pretended to be alive and made me—
Dialogue: 5,0:16:40.64,0:16:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm truly sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:45.94,0:16:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just didn't know
Dialogue: 5,0:16:48.66,0:16:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,that they'd all died a long time ago, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:53.20,0:16:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It might sound strange coming from me,
Dialogue: 5,0:16:55.68,0:16:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but don't hold it against them.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:58.35,0:16:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I would never.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:01.07,0:17:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:03.22,0:17:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't have a choice!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:09.21,0:17:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to interrupt this touching reunion.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:14.22,0:17:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't you think it'd make Humpnie real happy if we tortured Ai?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:17.70,0:17:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch her!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:27.28,0:17:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:28.19,0:17:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai, run!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:34.56,0:17:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:35.69,0:17:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:36.67,0:17:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't run away!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:37.79,0:17:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Not without saving you first, Father!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:41.78,0:17:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You brat—
Dialogue: 5,0:17:44.34,0:17:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite enough.{lol}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:52.28,0:17:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get full of yourselves!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:55.92,0:17:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Scar, I'll need some backup.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:58.32,0:17:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:15.55,0:18:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}I left in search of my lover.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:17.74,0:18:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}I never thought I'd find my daughter instead.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:25.08,0:18:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}Either way, damn that Hana.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:28.08,0:18:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}She just up and vanished,
Dialogue: 5,0:18:29.46,0:18:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}gave birth to a kid,
Dialogue: 5,0:18:31.52,0:18:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}and died.{selfishly}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:36.45,0:18:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}I have a daughter.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:38.89,0:18:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}It doesn't even feel real{ at all}.{hasn't hit me}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:41.75,0:18:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}It's just not me.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:44.60,0:18:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}I simply can't be
Dialogue: 5,0:18:47.39,0:18:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}a good father.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:48.89,0:18:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:49.87,0:18:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:50.85,0:18:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Scar?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:01.22,0:19:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:05.13,0:19:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you forget?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:06.53,0:19:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't die.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:08.22,0:19:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:11.16,0:19:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}Good grief.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:12.81,0:19:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}Kids are such a pain.{troublesome}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:17.33,0:19:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:18.48,0:19:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:19.62,0:19:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't told you my real name yet, have I?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:23.56,0:19:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I never even told your mother.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:28.83,0:19:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Kizuna Astin.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:34.14,0:19:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're Ai Astin.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:39.21,0:19:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai... Astin.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:42.88,0:19:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What a nice name.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:02.05,0:20:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:04.38,0:20:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:05.96,0:20:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:08.27,0:20:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:09.77,0:20:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}Damn it.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:12.76,0:20:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}I've got so many things left to say.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:18.12,0:20:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}It's no use.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:19.49,0:20:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}I'm too sleepy.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:24.49,0:20:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}I don't wanna die.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:35.54,0:20:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}And thus,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:44.55,Nichiyoubi,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\an4\shad2.5\blur0.8\fscx30\fscy30\pos(38,40)}And thus,
Dialogue: 5,0:20:36.70,0:20:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}after losing his wife,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.84,0:20:44.55,Nichiyoubi,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\an4\shad2.5\blur0.8\fscx30\fscy30\pos(166,40)}after losing his wife,
Dialogue: 5,0:20:38.34,0:20:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}making his daughter cry,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.34,0:20:44.55,Nichiyoubi,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\an4\shad2.5\blur0.8\fscx30\fscy30\pos(412,40)}making his daughter cry,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.96,0:20:44.55,Nichiyoubi,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\an4\shad2.5\blur0.8\fscx30\fscy30\pos(718,40)}being seen off by a friend and a gravekeeper,
Dialogue: 5,0:20:40.02,0:20:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}being seen off by a friend and a gravekeeper,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.72,0:20:44.55,Nichiyoubi,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\an4\shad2.5\blur0.8\fscx30\fscy30\pos(478,410)}and leaving behind regrets,
Dialogue: 5,0:20:42.73,0:20:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}and leaving behind regrets,
