Dialogue: 5,0:20:53.73,0:20:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}Father then awakened dead.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:03.30,0:21:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}He loved humans more than anyone else did
Dialogue: 5,0:21:05.69,0:21:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}and hated the dead more than anyone else, too,
